18.
31Nahetu kusalo dhammo nahetussa kusalassa dhammassa āhārapaccayena paccayo…  tīṇi.
19.
32Hetu kusalo dhammo hetussa kusalassa dhammassa indriyapaccayena paccayo…  nava.
20.
33Nahetu kusalo dhammo nahetussa kusalassa dhammassa jhānapaccayena paccayo…  tīṇi.
21.
34Hetu kusalo dhammo hetussa kusalassa dhammassa maggapaccayena paccayo…  nava.
22.
35Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe nava, nissaye nava, upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi, indriye nava, jhāne tīṇi, magge nava, sampayutte nava, atthiyā nava, natthiyā nava, vigate nava, avigate nava.
